00:20:06.788 --> 00:20:09.416
I'm a savage!

374
00:20:09.541 --> 00:20:11.335
Whatever I want.
I'm going to get!

375
00:20:11.418 --> 00:20:13.754
Whatever I want.
I'm have to get!

